EdgeNest-最终方案.md
# Stray repo-root binary from `go build ./cmd/edgenest`. Anchored with a
# leading slash so it ignores only a top-level ./edgenest, NOT the source
# package dir cmd/edgenest/ (the bare pattern matched both). Normal build
# output lands in bin/ and dist/, already ignored above.
/edgenest
